{"tid":1700191,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[行動]  小心閉路電視","createTime":"2019-11-08T11:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:55:44.000Z","uid":54243,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b23e4480da476ec8ecef125eec98c293324f982","tid":1700191,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"近排好多手足唔係現場被捕 係被人check 閉路跟到<br />\n講真 你把遮開到幾大都一定遮唔哂<br />\n治本方法 搞掂d 閉路 <br />\n由今日開始 見到所有屬於政府既閉路一律有機會就裝修 裝修唔到都搵機會塗黑左佢  當然做野前確保自己安全可以走得甩先 有信心先做 無信心既寧願唔做 不被捕係大原則<br />\n而藍店同中立店就自己諗啦 唔俾意見<br />\n黃店我相信d 閉路會日日清<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時無野做既 得閒係目標物附近街坊look 行下 搵下有咩逃生路線最安全 tg 哨兵永遠唔夠你親身經驗咁準<br />\n做完野記得兜多幾次路先返去 <br />\n做完野後有 「熱心」路人想阻止你既 打一拳就走唔好戀戰 留多一分鐘 就多一分鐘危險 <br />\n<br />\n祝不再被捕"},{"pid":"303e72b4a6f2d0386bc8eb7d3ac3e8983e6aac66","tid":1700191,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"549445749bb2b15a8b3a4aa1faa90f3b200a3328","tid":1700191,"uid":24707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c165a9021145b75c45518772e634b141e10279","tid":1700191,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"。。。想重啟十點尻叫 麻煩入嚟睇睇。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db6fa8aab0c89255e90c5d85cc78b4b29cef92c3","tid":1700191,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n香港人 報仇"},{"pid":"74e890016dc370696de837fbb98efca5960a64cb","tid":1700191,"uid":275640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"662fda6e856b02f8456ce8735797d7737d4b90c4","tid":1700191,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26fda8